{"tid":154465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩！大專討論下港獨都唔比","createTime":"2017-03-13T10:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T22:29:16.000Z","uid":72262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abef9006cf5d3a75b35a200fa70a0310daec4738","tid":154465,"uid":72262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"香港文匯報訊（記者　溫仲綺）再有大專學生打「自由」的旗號，在校園內宣揚違法「港獨」訊息。疑有明愛專上學院學生在校內「民主牆」貼上印有「香港獨立」字眼的宣傳品，其後校方以不恰當、破壞學校聲譽、影響學校發展及辦學機構籌募捐款等因由，要求涉事者除去宣傳品以遏止歪風。涉事者則聲言「民主牆」是學生「自由發表意見」的平台，不代表院校立場，校方沒有資格審查內容云云。有教育界人士指出，政治勢力的操控，令校園「港獨」苟延殘喘，校方有責任處理採取措施，維護學校的聲譽及學生利益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/03/11/HK1703110003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2FHK1703110003.htm&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=684ff215\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/03/11/HK1703110003.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f3dbf7ca9cde32b0d973e380e4c61d57132308dc","tid":154465,"uid":72262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cihehkss/posts/558886160979446:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcihehkss%2Fposts%2F558886160979446%3A0&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=ed840237\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cihehkss/posts/558886160979446:0</a><br />\n又寫得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8670e19ce625d39d63adb098d5fc813005b0006e","tid":154465,"uid":72262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人讀呢間學校知道而家咩情況？"},{"pid":"c34840f11d577878a3706b142d3aea4abb22a1fa","tid":154465,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T21:00:22.000Z","msg":"間間大專都開始中學化小學化幼稚園化"},{"pid":"2265eeefad02185c15636c84ef4565ebcf8ae15d","tid":154465,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T